wants to buy Starry Theatrical Club

25
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,520
in exchange for Ou Si Ke to quit Shi Lan Ke.

26
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:09,840
Grandfather wants me to tell you

27
00:02:10,359 --> 00:02:11,319
