very expensive?

42
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,000
It's not that expensive actually.

43
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:40,239
The Soul Masters are the most important
in Douluo Continent.

44
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,799
