91
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:40,719
Just a brief understanding would do.

92
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,520
Ou Si Ke, you're back.

93
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,480
Did you buy the stuff?

94
00:04:51,559 --> 00:04:52,319
Where's Chief Ning?

95
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,680
My dad has already departed to Martial Soul City.

96
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,719
Has the final not started yet?

97
00:04:56,879 --> 00:04:57,839
He said he wanted to go earlier

98
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:59,839
and see whether he could find
something fishy in the contest.

99
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:01,920
What's the matter?
Are you looking for him?

100
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:05,960
I have something to tell you guys.

101
00:05:07,999 --> 00:05:08,879
You must stay calm

102
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,119
