103
00:05:10,719 --> 00:05:11,240
What's wrong?

104
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:14,480
Prince Xue Xing came
to see me in person.

105
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:17,559
What happened then?

106
00:05:19,559 --> 00:05:20,240
That's it.

107
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,200
This is not a big deal.

108
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,360
Why do you want us to stay calm?

109
00:05:23,839 --> 00:05:24,999
No. Don't you get it?

110
00:05:24,999 --> 00:05:26,839
Prince Xue Xing came
to see me in person.

111
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:28,200
You know...

112
00:05:28,319 --> 00:05:30,119
He always goes against us.

113
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,760
We already know that.

114
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:35,960
Then,

115
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,119
he gave me an ownership transfer letter.

116
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:40,200
He said he wanted to give me

117
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:42,279
an incredible theatrical club.

118
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,760
That's the theatrical club
that I've always wanted.

119
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:46,119
Maybe...

120
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,200
You guys can never imagine

121
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:49,439
how great that theatrical club is.

122
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,559
Starry Theatrical Club.

123
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:53,399
One of the three largest theatrical clubs
in Tian Dou City, right?

124
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:55,520
How did you know that?

125
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,159
Did you accept it?

126
00:05:57,599 --> 00:05:58,559
Of course...

127
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,559
I did not accept it.

128
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:01,719
Why?

129
00:06:02,439 --> 00:06:03,159
Why?

130
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,839
Can I betray Shi Lan Ke?

131
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:07,200
How is this betrayal?

132
00:06:07,599 --> 00:06:09,040
Besides, you were supposed to quit in the first place.

133
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,480
The theatrical club is a present

134
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,839
from the Prince.

135
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:20,559
I want to stay here.

136
00:06:23,279 --> 00:06:25,960
Aren't arts your dream?

137
00:06:26,159 --> 00:06:26,920
That's right.

138
00:06:29,999 --> 00:06:30,920
I'm an orphan.

139
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:34,480
Headmaster found me
and has raised me since childhood.

140
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:35,680
Since young, I've always hoped

141
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,119
that I could have a very powerful Martial Soul.

142
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,999
But I became like this

143
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,680
