The Food Branch Martial Soul is very powerful.

145
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,200
Every time I used my Martial Soul,

146
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:49,240
I would dress like a chef,

147
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,279
carrying the bucket

148
00:06:50,719 --> 00:06:52,080
and giving out sausages.

149
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,119
