wanted us to enter the final.

389
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:41,680
That's the truth.

390
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:42,800
I wasn't lying.

391
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:45,119
I think

392
00:19:45,119 --> 00:19:45,920
