409
00:20:28,200 --> 00:20:28,800
you are

410
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:30,840
the most important person to me.

411
00:20:43,080 --> 00:20:44,119
Ye Zhi Qiu gave me this

412
00:20:44,759 --> 00:20:46,479
