413
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:48,680
Let's go together.

414
00:20:51,479 --> 00:20:51,920
All right.

415
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:53,359
I promise you.

416
00:20:54,040 --> 00:20:55,359
